<topic id="how-to-mysql">
  <title>How to Configure MySQL Support</title>
  <body>
    <p>Follow this procedure to configure the support for a MySQL database:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-mysql-datasource.dita#configure-mysql-datasource">Configure
          a MySQL <term>Data Source</term> driver.</xref></li>
      <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-mysql-connection.dita#configure-mysql-connection">Configure
          a MySQL <term>Connection</term>.</xref></li>
      <li>Use the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view from the <menucascade>
          <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol>
        </menucascade> menu or switch to the <uicontrol>Database Perspective</uicontrol> (available
        from <menucascade>
          <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
        </menucascade>).</li>
    </ol>
  </body>
